Steps to create initial project
1. Create a directory and create virtual environment
python -m venv djenv

2. Activate virtual environment
source djenv/bin/activate

3. Install Django
pip install django

4. Check if it is installed
django-admin --version

5. Create a project
django-admin startproject sample

6. Go into project directory
cd sample

7. Create django app
python manage.py startapp appname

8. To start server
python manage.py runserver
